we▁ find▁ that▁ $I4_1/amd$▁ is▁ dynamically▁ stable▁ at▁ pressures▁ above▁ about▁ $250$▁ ,▁ and▁ therefore▁ we▁ perform▁ calculations▁ in▁ the▁ pressure▁ range▁ $250$▁ $1000$▁ The▁ speed▁ of▁ sound▁ as▁ function▁ of▁ pressure▁ and▁ density▁ reported▁ in▁ \ref{abinitio}▁ corresponds▁ to▁ the▁ highest▁ energy▁ acoustic▁ branch▁ and▁ is▁ averaged▁ over▁ stochastic▁ all▁ generated▁ directions▁ in▁ $\mathbf{q}$▁ space▁ \begin{figure}
